&control
   calculation='nscf',
   prefix='FeO',
   outdir='./data/'
   pseudo_dir = '/yourdir/PSPOT/',
/
&system
   ibrav=0,
   nat=4,
   ntyp=3,
   ecutwfc = 50.0,
   ecutrho = 500.0,
   occupations='tetrahedra',
   nspin=2,
   nbnd=40,
   starting_magnetization(2)= 0.5,
   starting_magnetization(3)=-0.5,
   starting_ns_eigenvalue(3,2,2)=1.0, 
   starting_ns_eigenvalue(3,1,3)=1.0,
/
 &electrons 
/
CELL_PARAMETERS angstrom
 2.16698  2.16698  4.33396
 2.16698  4.33396  2.16698
 4.33396  2.16698  2.16698

ATOMIC_SPECIES
 O    16.00  o_pbe_v1.2.uspp.F.UPF
 Fe1  55.85  fe_pbe_v1.5.uspp.F.UPF
 Fe2  55.85  fe_pbe_v1.5.uspp.F.UPF

ATOMIC_POSITIONS crystal
 O   0.25 0.25 0.25
 O   0.75 0.75 0.75
 Fe1 0.0  0.0  0.0
 Fe2 0.5  0.5  0.5


K_POINTS automatic
 12 12 12 0 0 0

HUBBARD (ortho-atomic)
 U Fe1-3d 4.0
 U Fe2-3d 4.0
